<p class=MsoListParagraph style='text-align:justify'><span lang=MS
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>The
physical assessment will take into account cumulative quarterly performance
over a financial year period.</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:0in;text-align:justify'><span
lang=MS style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:0in;text-align:justify'><span
lang=MS style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>1.6.3 <b>Overall
Ranking of performance</b></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:0in;text-align:justify'><span
lang=MS style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;text-indent:
.5in'><span lang=MS style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;
color:black'>The overall ranking of performance will involve:</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:
-.25in'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>a)<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span
lang=EN-GB style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Collating
of the results obtained in the Form A and B, and obtaining a simple arithmetic
mean. </span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:
-.25in'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>b)<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span
lang=EN-GB style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>The
arithmetic mean will in effect constitute the final aggregate performance mark.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:
-.25in'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>c)<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span
lang=EN-GB style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>The
aggregate mark will be classified according to the pre-arranged criteria for
performance rating indicated in the table below.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:
-.25in'><span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>d)<span
style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span
lang=EN-GB style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>60
per cent is the minimum acceptable aggregate delivery level.</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:0in;text-align:justify'><span
style='font-size:12.0pt;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif;color:black'></span></p>

